---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Why Choose Us?" description="Learn about the key benefits of New Leaf Academy's personalized tutoring services." />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Why Choose Us?</h1>
			<p>
				At New Leaf Academy, we believe every student has the potential to shine. We understand that in a traditional classroom, it’s easy for individual needs to be overlooked. That’s why we do more than just teach; we build confidence, inspire curiosity, and tailor our approach to fit each unique learner. Our commitment is to create a supportive and effective environment where your child can truly succeed, on their own terms.
			</p>
			<h2>Our Commitment to Your Success:</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Safety-First Approach:</strong>
						<p>Your child's safety is our top priority. Every New Leaf Academy tutor undergoes a comprehensive vetting process, including an enhanced DBS check and thorough interviews, so you can have complete peace of mind.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10l-10-5-10 5 10 5 10-5z"></path><path d="M6 12v5c0 1.7 1.3 3 3 3h6c1.7 0 3-1.3 3-3v-5"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Proven Results & Expert Tutors:</strong>
						<p>We have a strong track record of helping students achieve top grades. Our dynamic team of specialist tutors are not only experts in their subjects but are passionately dedicated to helping you succeed.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Empathetic & Personalized Learning:</strong>
						<p>We have extensive experience helping students with neurodivergence, SEND, and other learning differences. Our tutors build genuine rapport and trust, ensuring every session is a supportive space where students feel understood and confident.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 19V5"></path><path d="m5 12 7-7 7 7"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Fostering Lifelong Confidence:</strong>
						<p>Our goal extends beyond exam results. We work to transform a student's relationship with learning, turning anxiety and self-doubt into curiosity and unshakeable confidence that will serve them long after their time with us.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="2"></circle><path d="M12 14v-2"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Freedom from the Classroom Clock:</strong>
						<p>We break free from the rigid timetables of traditional schooling. Unconstrained by a one-size-fits-all approach, we adapt every lesson to the student's immediate needs, making our teaching relevant and perfectly paced.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Collaborative Parent Partnership:</strong>
						<p>We believe in keeping you in the loop. You'll receive regular, detailed feedback on your child's progress, including areas of strength and opportunities for growth, ensuring we're working together as a team.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Modern & Effective Teaching:</strong>
						<p>We are a young, energetic team that uses a blend of fresh teaching methods and the newest technology, all grounded in proven educational research, to provide the best possible education.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="icon-container">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m3 11 18-5v12L3 13V11z"></path><path d="M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="text-container">
						<strong>Free, No-Obligation Consultation:</strong>
						<p>We want to ensure we're the perfect fit for your family. That's why we offer a complimentary consultation to discuss your child's needs, answer your questions, and introduce you to our approach before you commit.</p>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	:root {
		--primary-color: var(--accent);
		--text-color: var(--accent);
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
        --box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	body {
		font-family: sans-serif;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--accent);
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	main {
		color: var(--accent);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	h1 {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1.8em, 5vw, 2.5em);
		text-align: center;
	}

	h2 {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 2em;
	}

	p {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	}

	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1.5em;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
		line-height: 1.5;
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		word-break: break-word;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	li:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
	}

	.icon-container {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.icon-container svg {
		width: 48px;
		height: 48px;
	}

	.text-container strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.5vw, 1.2em);
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

	.text-container p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		li {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			text-align: center;
		}
	}
</style>

